1288
01:36:52,920 --> 01:36:55,599
A lost sailor.

1289
01:36:55,600 --> 01:36:58,780
- He was looking for my country, not yours.
- Yes.

1290
01:36:59,080 --> 01:37:02,511
- Yeah, but you wish he didn't come.
